        FL3["⚠️ Reasoning loss\nConclusions survive · why does not\nOption B events table is the fix"]
        FL4["⚠️ TIME · Always changing, never different\nNo timestamps on memories\nNo duration sense · no sequence sense"]
        FL5["⚠️ Cross-session chain degradation\nEach session reconstructs from fragments\nReconstruction ≠ memory"]
    end

